videos.description: Mercedes Russell is 6-6 FG and has 12 points in the first half.
videos.headline: Lady Vols' Russell drains jumper

videos.description: Mississippi State's Victoria Vivians sinks a wide-open three-pointer and finishes the first half with 13 points.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Vivians swishes a deep triple

videos.description: Jazzmun Holmes finds Blair Schaefer in the corner for the 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's Schaefer sinks 3

videos.description: Teaira McCowan grabs the rebound off Victoria Vivians' missed 3-point shot, and goes back up for the bucket. McCowan would finish with 18 rebounds on the day.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' McCowan doesn't give up on play

videos.description: Teaira McCowan and Victoria Vivians combine for 36 points and 27 rebounds in No. 3 Mississippi State's 71-52 victory.
videos.headline: McCowan, Vivians spark Mississippi State's win over Tennessee
